Name: Cafe Welling
Review Text: Loved this little place tucked into a cute little corner street. The ambiance was amazing and we tried the best beef and pork sausages here. The owner is very friendly and warm and for that reason we spent a lot of time there chatting and enjoying the beer. Would highly recommend it to everyone.

Name: Cafe Welling
Review Text: This is the real deal! One of the last true cafes of Amsterdam! Where they served drinks and munchies and where it used to be allowed to smoke inside and the walls became brown!

Name: Cafe Welling
Review Text: A nice cafe around the museums neighborhood with a warm classic atmosphere. Be careful, some international credit cards are not taken.

Name: Cafe Welling

Name: Cafe Welling

Name: Cafe Welling

Name: Cafe Welling

Name: Cafe Welling
